test suite.

This module is the async analogue of the ``MockSocket`` helper used by
``tests/maint_notifications/test_maint_notifications_handling.py``. Instead of
patching ``socket.socket``, it patches ``asyncio.open_connection`` (the call made
by ``redis.asyncio.connection.Connection._connect``) and hands back a real
``asyncio.StreamReader`` paired with a scripted writer double. Responses (and, for
maintenance notifications tests, RESP3 push frames) are fed directly into the
reader's buffer as soon as a command is "sent", so no real sockets, threads, or
selectors are involved.
